Add sideEffects flag for Webpack, fixes #155

Add TypeScript type definitions

RE:DOM has working TypeScript type definitions in the DefinitelyTyped
repository. Since they work very well, they could be shipped with the
RE:DOM package itself.

This adds an copy of the current type definitions from DefinitelyTyped
repository into the RE:DOM repository.
